---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Section from '../components/ui/Section.astro';
import Button from '../components/ui/Button.astro';
import Hero from '../components/ui/Hero.astro';
import Card from '../components/ui/Card.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="About - Fund Investigator"
  description="Our mission is to make institutional-grade mutual fund analysis accessible to every Indian investor."
>
  <Hero size="md">
    <h1 class="text-display-xl font-bold text-navy mb-6">
      Why We Built <span class="text-gold">Fund Investigator</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-body-lg text-secondary-gray leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Moving beyond simple star ratings to understand the <i>true</i> drivers of mutual fund performance.
    </p>
  </Hero>

  <Section background="white" spacing="lg" maxWidth="md">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-navy font-bold">The Information Gap</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray leading-relaxed">
        For years, retail investors in India have been sold mutual funds based on a single metric: <strong>Past Returns</strong>.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray leading-relaxed">
        But returns tell only half the story. Missing from the conversation:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-none pl-0 space-y-4 my-8">
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray">How much risk the manager took to achieve those returns.</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray">How the fund behaves during market crashes (drawdowns).</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex gap-4 items-start">
          <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12"/></svg>
          </div>
          <span class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray">Whether a "Growth" fund has silently drifted into "Value" territory.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray leading-relaxed">
        Institutional investors have access to expensive terminals and analysts to answer these questions. <strong>Fund Investigator provides those same insights at no cost.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="cream" spacing="lg" maxWidth="xl">
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-heading-lg font-bold text-navy mb-4">Our Core Principles</h2>
      <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-gold mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <Card variant="bordered" padding="lg" hover={false}>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-heading-md font-bold text-navy mb-3">Facts, Not Opinions</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray">Mathematical evidence—Sharpe ratios, Beta, Alpha—presented without recommendations. The analysis speaks for itself.</p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="bordered" padding="lg" hover={false}>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-heading-md font-bold text-navy mb-3">Zero Conflict of Interest</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray">Not a broker, not a distributor. No commissions, no hidden incentives. Data accuracy is the only measure of success.</p>
      </Card>

      <Card variant="bordered" padding="lg" hover={false}>
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-navy/10 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-navy" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19.428 15.428a2 2 0 00-1.022-.547l-2.384-.477a6 6 0 00-3.86.517l-.318.158a6 6 0 01-3.86.517L6.05 15.21a2 2 0 00-1.806.547M8 4h8l-1 1v5.172a2 2 0 00.586 1.414l5 5c1.26 1.26.367 3.414-1.415 3.414H4.828c-1.782 0-2.674-2.154-1.414-3.414l5-5A2 2 0 009 10.172V5L8 4z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-heading-md font-bold text-navy mb-3">Scientific Rigor</h3>
        <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray">Data sourced directly from AMFI and public disclosures. Calculations follow standard financial models and industry practices.</p>
      </Card>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="white" spacing="lg" maxWidth="md">
    <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-heading-lg text-navy font-bold">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray leading-relaxed">
        Fund Investigator exists to democratize access to institutional-grade investment analysis. The full picture behind mutual fund performance—risk-adjusted returns, drawdown behavior, and style drift—should be accessible to all investors, not just institutions with expensive terminals.
      </p>
      <p class="text-body-md text-secondary-gray leading-relaxed">
        Built on transparent data sources and rigorous financial models, this platform provides the facts needed for informed decisions—without conflicts of interest or hidden agendas.
      </p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 mt-8">
        <a href="mailto:contact@fundinvestigator.com" class="text-navy hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium text-body-sm flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          Contact Us
        </a>
        <a href="https://twitter.com/fundinvestigator" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-navy hover:text-gold transition-colors font-medium text-body-sm flex items-center gap-2">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"/></svg>
          Follow on X
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Section>

  <Section background="cream" spacing="lg" maxWidth="md">
    <div class="text-center">
      <h2 class="text-heading-lg font-bold text-navy mb-6">See the Analysis in Action</h2>
      <Button href="https://deepdive.fundinvestigator.com" size="lg" icon="arrow-right">Launch Deepdive</Button>
    </div>
  </Section>
</Layout>